article.description: — Jahmyl Telfort had 20 points in Northeastern's 66-46 win over Georgia State on Sunday.
article.headline: Telfort's 20 help Northeastern beat Georgia State 66-46
article.linkText: Telfort's 20 help Northeastern beat Georgia State 66-46
article.story: BOSTON -- — Jahmyl Telfort had 20 points in Northeastern's 66-46 win over Georgia State on Sunday. Telfort also added six rebounds for the Huskies (2-6). Alexander Nwagha scored 15 points and added 14 rebounds. Ja'Heim Hudson led the Panthers (5-4) in scoring, finishing with 11 points, eight rebounds and two blocks. Georgia State also got 10 points from Brenden Tucker. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
